---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="Servicios">

<div class="menu-placeholder"></div>

<div id="scroll-trigger" style="height: 1px; position: absolute; top: 120px;"></div>



<main class="container_main">
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header-section">
            <div class="production-slate">
                <div class="slate-header">
                    <span class="production-title">SERVICIOS</span>
                    <span class="production-company">CASA PRODUCTORA</span>
                </div>
                <div class="slate-divider"></div>
                <p class="production-tagline">
                    "Cada proyecto es una historia esperando ser contada"
                </p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="services-screenplay">
            <div class="screenplay-page">
                <div class="page-header">
                    <span class="page-number">1.</span>
                    <span class="scene-heading">INT. ESTUDIO - DÍA</span>
                </div>

                <div class="service-scene">
                    <div class="scene-number">ESCENA 01</div>
                    <h2 class="service-title">PRODUCCIÓN AUDIOVISUAL</h2>
                    <div class="action-line">
                        Desde la primera idea garabateada en una servilleta hasta los créditos finales que ruedan en pantalla. El proceso completo: desarrollo de concepto, preproducción meticulosa, rodaje profesional y postproducción de nivel cinematográfico.
                    </div>
                    <div class="technical-specs">
                        <span class="spec">• Desarrollo creativo integral</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Preproducción completa</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Rodaje 4K/6K/8K</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Post-producción avanzada</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="screenplay-page">
                <div class="page-header">
                    <span class="page-number">2.</span>
                    <span class="scene-heading">EXT. LOCACIÓN - GOLDEN HOUR</span>
                </div>

                <div class="service-scene">
                    <div class="scene-number">ESCENA 02</div>
                    <h2 class="service-title">VIDEOCLIPS MUSICALES</h2>
                    <div class="action-line">
                        La música cobra vida visual. Cada beat se convierte en un corte, cada melodía en una composición de cuadro. Trabajamos con artistas para materializar su universo sonoro en imágenes que trascienden lo convencional.
                    </div>
                    <div class="technical-specs">
                        <span class="spec">• Dirección artística especializada</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Conceptualización visual</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Cinematografía musical</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Color grading avanzado</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="screenplay-page">
                <div class="page-header">
                    <span class="page-number">3.</span>
                    <span class="scene-heading">INT. AGENCIA - NOCHE</span>
                </div>

                <div class="service-scene">
                    <div class="scene-number">ESCENA 03</div>
                    <h2 class="service-title">COMERCIALES & BRANDED CONTENT</h2>
                    <div class="action-line">
                        Más allá de la publicidad tradicional. Creamos narrativas que conectan marcas con audiencias a través de historias auténticas. Cada pieza es un cortometraje que vende sin vender, que emociona mientras informa.
                    </div>
                    <div class="technical-specs">
                        <span class="spec">• Estrategia narrativa</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Branded storytelling</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Producción multiplataforma</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Distribución estratégica</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="screenplay-page">
                <div class="page-header">
                    <span class="page-number">4.</span>
                    <span class="scene-heading">EXT. MUNDO REAL - CONTINUO</span>
                </div>

                <div class="service-scene">
                    <div class="scene-number">ESCENA 04</div>
                    <h2 class="service-title">DOCUMENTALES Y REPORTAJES</h2>
                    <div class="action-line">
                        La realidad como materia prima, el cine como herramienta. Documentamos historias reales con la sensibilidad visual del cine de autor. Cada testimonio es tratado como una confesión íntima, cada imagen como un cuadro deliberado.
                    </div>
                    <div class="technical-specs">
                        <span class="spec">• Investigación profunda</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Narrativa documental</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Cinematografía verité</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Edición narrativa</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="screenplay-page">
                <div class="page-header">
                    <span class="page-number">5.</span>
                    <span class="scene-heading">INT. EVENTO - TIEMPO REAL</span>
                </div>

                <div class="service-scene">
                    <div class="scene-number">ESCENA 05</div>
                    <h2 class="service-title">COBERTURA DE EVENTOS PREMIUM</h2>
                    <div class="action-line">
                        Momentos únicos capturados con la precisión de un director de fotografía. No documentamos eventos, creamos películas en tiempo real. Cada celebración se convierte en una experiencia cinematográfica memorable.
                    </div>
                    <div class="technical-specs">
                        <span class="spec">• Cobertura multicámara</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Streaming profesional</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Edición en vivo</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Fotografía de Evento</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="screenplay-page">
                <div class="page-header">
                    <span class="page-number">6.</span>
                    <span class="scene-heading">INT. ESTUDIO CREATIVO - ATEMPORAL</span>
                </div>

                <div class="service-scene">
                    <div class="scene-number">ESCENA 06</div>
                    <h2 class="service-title">PRODUCCIÓN CREATIVA PERSONALIZADA</h2>
                    <div class="action-line">
                        Proyectos únicos requieren enfoques únicos. Desde fashion films hasta instalaciones audiovisuales, desde arte conceptual hasta contenido institucional. Cada brief es una oportunidad de explorar nuevos lenguajes visuales.
                    </div>
                    <div class="technical-specs">
                        <span class="spec">• Consultoría especializada</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Desarrollo a medida</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Equipos multidisciplinarios</span>
                        <span class="spec">• Acompañamiento integral</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="final-scene">
            <div class="screenplay-page">
                <div class="page-header">
                    <span class="scene-heading">FADE TO BLACK.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="final-dialogue">
                    <p class="character-name">PRODUCTOR</p>
                    <p class="dialogue">
                        ¿Listo para escribir la siguiente escena juntos?
                    </p>
                    <a href="#contacto" class="cta-button">
                        ACCIÓN →
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</main>
</Layout>

<style>
    :root {
        --paper-white: #f8f8f6;
        --ink-black: #1a1a1a;
        --typewriter-blue: #0066cc;
        --red-ink: #cc0000;
        --pencil-gray: #666666;
        --margin-line: #e0e0e0;
        --shadow-soft: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        --paper-texture: #f5f5f3;
    }

    /* Animaciones y keyframes */
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes slideInFromLeft {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-50px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes typewriter {
        from {
            width: 0;
        }
        to {
            width: 100%;
        }
    }

    @keyframes subtleFloat {
        0%, 100% {
            transform: translateY(0px);
        }
        50% {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
    }

    @keyframes gentleGlow {
        0%, 100% {
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
        }
        50% {
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.2);
        }
    }

    @keyframes paperBreathe {
        0%, 100% {
            transform: scale(1);
        }
        50% {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }
    }

    /* Smooth scrolling */
    html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    /* Estilos generales con animaciones */
    .menu-placeholder {
        height: 140px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #000000 100%);
        border-bottom: 3px solid var(--red-ink);
        animation: slideInFromLeft 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    .container_main {
        min-height: 100vh;
        background: var(--paper-white);
        position: relative;
        font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.2s forwards;
    }

    .container_main::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background-image:
            repeating-linear-gradient(
                transparent,
                transparent 24px,
                var(--margin-line) 24px,
                var(--margin-line) 25px
            ),
            linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 80px, var(--red-ink) 80px, var(--red-ink) 81px, transparent 81px);
        opacity: 0.3;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .header-section {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.4s forwards;
    }

    .production-slate {
        background: var(--ink-black);
        color: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        position: relative;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px var(--shadow-soft);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        animation: gentleGlow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .production-slate:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .slate-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .production-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .production-title::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 2px;
        background: var(--typewriter-blue);
        animation: typewriter 2s ease-out 1s forwards;
    }

    .production-company {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .production-company:hover {
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .slate-divider {
        height: 2px;
        background: white;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        transform: scaleX(0);
        animation: typewriter 1.5s ease-out 1.2s forwards;
    }

    .production-tagline {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-style: italic;
        opacity: 0.9;
        margin: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 1.8s both;
    }

    .services-screenplay {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .screenplay-page {
        background: white;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-left: 3px solid var(--red-ink);
        box-shadow:
            2px 2px 10px var(--shadow-soft),
            inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(50px);
        animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
    }

    /* Delay progresivo para cada tarjeta */
    .screenplay-page:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
    .screenplay-page:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
    .screenplay-page:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.0s; }
    .screenplay-page:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }
    .screenplay-page:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }
    .screenplay-page:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 1.6s; }

    .screenplay-page:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.02);
        box-shadow: 
            0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15),
            inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
        border-left-color: var(--typewriter-blue);
    }

    .page-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--margin-line);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .page-header::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 1px;
        background: var(--typewriter-blue);
        transition: left 0.8s ease;
    }

    .screenplay-page:hover .page-header::after {
        left: 0;
    }

    .page-number {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: var(--pencil-gray);
        min-width: 30px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .screenplay-page:hover .page-number {
        color: var(--typewriter-blue);
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    .scene-heading {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: var(--ink-black);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        transition: letter-spacing 0.3s ease;
    }

    .screenplay-page:hover .scene-heading {
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .service-scene {
        position: relative;
        flex-grow: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .scene-number {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--pencil-gray);
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
    }

    .scene-number::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: -10px;
        top: 50%;
        width: 0;
        height: 2px;
        background: var(--typewriter-blue);
        transition: width 0.4s ease;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
    }

    .screenplay-page:hover .scene-number {
        color: var(--typewriter-blue);
        transform: translateX(15px);
    }

    .screenplay-page:hover .scene-number::before {
        width: 10px;
    }

    .service-title {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        color: var(--ink-black);
        margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        position: relative;
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }

    .service-title::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -5px;
        left: 0;
        width: 40px;
        height: 2px;
        background: var(--typewriter-blue);
        transition: width 0.4s ease;
    }

    .screenplay-page:hover .service-title {
        color: var(--typewriter-blue);
        letter-spacing: 3px;
    }

    .screenplay-page:hover .service-title::after {
        width: 80px;
    }

    .action-line {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--ink-black);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: justify;
        font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
        flex-grow: 1;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
    }

    .screenplay-page:hover .action-line {
        color: var(--pencil-gray);
    }

    .technical-specs {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin-top: auto;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        border-left: 2px solid var(--typewriter-blue);
        position: relative;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .screenplay-page:hover .technical-specs {
        padding-left: 2rem;
        border-left-width: 4px;
    }

    .spec {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--pencil-gray);
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        opacity: 0.8;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        transform: translateX(-5px);
    }

    .spec:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
    .spec:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
    .spec:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
    .spec:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.4s; }

    .screenplay-page:hover .spec {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
        color: var(--ink-black);
    }

    .final-scene {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 2s forwards;
    }

    .final-scene .screenplay-page {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        animation: subtleFloat 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        animation-delay: 2.5s;
    }

    .final-dialogue {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    .character-name {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: var(--ink-black);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 2.2s forwards;
    }

    .dialogue {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--ink-black);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-style: italic;
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 2.4s forwards;
    }

    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: var(--ink-black);
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
        border: 2px solid var(--ink-black);
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 2.6s forwards;
    }

    .cta-button::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent);
        transition: left 0.6s ease;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
        background: white;
        color: var(--ink-black);
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 
            0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2),
            0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .cta-button:hover::before {
        left: 100%;
    }

    .cta-button:active {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* Media queries sin cambios estructurales */
    @media (max-width: 1200px) {
        .services-screenplay {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .services-screenplay {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .screenplay-page {
            margin-left: 0;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }

        .scene-number {
            position: static;
            writing-mode: horizontal-tb;
            text-orientation: initial;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--typewriter-blue);
        }

        .production-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .slate-header {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .technical-specs {
            padding-left: 1rem;
        }

        .final-scene .screenplay-page {
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        /* Reducir animaciones en móvil */
        .screenplay-page:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.01);
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .services-screenplay {
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .screenplay-page {
            padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
        }
    }

    /* Reducir movimiento para usuarios que prefieren menos animación */
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        *,
        *::before,
        *::after {
            animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
            animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
            transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
            scroll-behavior: auto !important;
        }



    }



